## CI Pipeline (GitHub Actions)

```yaml
- name: Install uv
  uses: astral-sh/setup-uv@v3
  with:
    version: "latest"

- name: Install dependencies
  run: uv sync --frozen

- name: Lint
  run: uv run ruff check .

- name: Format check
  run: uv run ruff format --check .

- name: Type check
  run: uv run ty check  # or: uv run mypy . during transition

- name: Test
  run: uv run pytest tests/unit/ -v --tb=short --cov
```

The `--frozen` flag on `uv sync` ensures CI always uses the exact lockfile — no implicit updates.
